subtitle: I know and recognize my oneness with all
things I know that all form and all
circumstance are the creation of the
infant intelligence that is in and
around me I know that all things are the
result of conception and desire that my
world is ordered according to my own
thoughts and convictions
therefore I concentrate on harmony I see
nothing but order and constructiveness
all about me I do not accept thoughts of
destructiveness and disharmony in my
friends my loved ones and my fellow
workers I see nothing but cooperation
and assistance I know that we all seek
the same answers in the same goals I
know that each person must follow a
different path toward his vision and I
understand the searching and the coping
of everyone I know and see I have
sympathy and tolerance for all things in
all people I know that in as much as I
help others I help myself in my
brother's eye there is my own soul and
my friends smile there is my own humor
in my neighbor's sorrow there is my own
loss I have compassion and understanding
for all things for this life in which I
have been strives for understanding of
itself I deny air it is simply progress
towards truth I know that it is
impossible to fail when faith is present
I do not order things to be made in my
time or in my place but trust the
universal mind in its own great
knowledge of the time and place the need
in the way each moment of each day
brings my life closer to realization the
objects of my work are being
accomplished this very minute success
and harmony peace and confidence are
